data.description: Only ten minutes from historic downtown Columbia. This beautifully renovated brick style ranch sits in the heart of West Columbia. With lots of local shopping and restaurants close by. So are the interstate and main roads of 378 and US-1. This home features luxurious granite countertops and boasts a spacious lot size. This home also features new flooring, fresh interior paint job, and a beautiful master bathroom standing shower. This conveniently located and wonderfully renovated home is waiting for you to make it your own. Home qualifies for preferred lender closing cost credit program. Agent has a financial interest in property.
